@RoomService_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check
GET {{RoomService_HostAddress}}/_info
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Dummy Login - Admin
POST {{RoomService_HostAddress}}/dummyLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### 3. Dummy Login - User
POST {{RoomService_HostAddress}}/dummyLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "user"
}

###

### 4. Get All Rooms (требуется токен)
GET {{RoomService_HostAddress}}/rooms/list
Authorization: Bearer {eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..IsuV98GVbAaWy_qTQe3mjmA6RLECUJd0OElfmCMtaGc}
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Create Room (только admin)
POST {{RoomService_HostAddress}}/rooms/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..IsuV98GVbAaWy_qTQe3mjmA6RLECUJd0OElfmCMtaGc}

{
  "name": "Конференц-зал",
  "description": "Большой зал с проектором и доской",
  "capacity": 20
}

###

### 6. Create Another Room
POST {{RoomService_HostAddress}}/rooms/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Переговорка B",
  "description": "Для маленьких команд",
  "capacity": 6
}

###

### 7. Create Room with invalid data (должен вернуть 400)
POST {{RoomService_HostAddress}}/rooms/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Пустое имя"
}

###